@startuml
title SomeTrails Trail Search

actor User

participant "Explore Trails" as Explore
participant "Search Bar" as Search
participant "Map" as Map
participant "Trail Info Display" as Display
participant "Trails Storage Server" as Trails

== Explore Trails ==
User -> Explore: Request filtering for trails
Explore -> Trails: Filter trails
Trails -> Display: Display all trails filtered
Map -> Explore: Highlight trails
Explore -> User: Request input
== Search Specific Trail ==
User -> Search: Request trail information
Search -> Trails: Get trail information
Trails -> Display: Display trail information
Display -> Map: Move to trail location
Map -> User: Request input

@enduml
